Human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves. Small groups analyze which recruiters seemed most enthusiastic, and announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair.

An aroma of coffee and catered snacks spreads from the lounge, while a robotics startup captures attention by flying a small drone above its booth.
